Wrapper class: is a class that allows to store primitive data as object

prirmitive data --------> Corresponding wrapper class
int                       Integer
double                    Double
long                      Long
char                      Charcter
String                    String

Auto-boxing
1.General variable
Integer myInt = 8;
2.Aarray
Integer[] myIntArr = new Integer[10];
myIntArr[0] = 8;

Auto-unboxing
int value1 = myInt;
int value2 = myIntArr[0];
